headline: Dover Fueling Solutions Introduces Wayne PWR DC Fast Chargers with NACS Cable Option to Enhance the EV Charging Experience
summary: Dover Fueling Solutions ("DFS"), a part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a leading global provider of advanced customer-focused technologies, services and solutions in the fuel and convenience retail industries, today announced the addition of a North American Charging Standard (NACS) cable option to its Wayne PWR™ DC fast charger.
